{"tid":1542714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳智庫：中國買Twitter色情帳號 發佈香港假消息","createTime":"2019-09-05T02:44:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T02:58:15.000Z","uid":54373,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"933b539cdca38ee46546787837ecaf4885b0575d","tid":1542714,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:44:19.000Z","msg":"〔編譯陳成良／綜合報導〕澳洲戰略政策研究所（Australian Strategic Policy Institute, ASPI）3日發表一項報告，指社群媒體巨頭推特（Twitter）過去多年封鎖940個發放假消息的中國帳戶，指它們針對批評中國政府的知名異議人士，包括流亡海外的中國商人郭文貴。值得注意的是，該研究發現，中國在推特往往利用色情帳號發佈香港假消息，而且這些帳號很便宜就能買到。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_2906147_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_2906147_1.jpg&h=783bf2b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n    澳洲智庫的研究發現，中國利用廉價買到的低俗色情推特帳號，散佈香港假新聞。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n報告指出，研究人員整理了上述帳號所發布的360萬則貼文後，發現受影響帳號在至少2年間展開了「有影響能力的活動」，並稱它們的行動針對郭文貴等中國異議人士，其中來自618個帳號的3.8萬則貼文直接與郭文貴有關，內容圍繞着他與北京不和、及與美國前白宮首席策略師班農的關係。<br />\n<br />\n分析發現，其中一些帳號在散播香港假消息之前，發表不少色情、足球和韓國流行音樂（K-pop）有關的推文內容，最明顯的就是色情，平均每四個轉發最多的推文中至少有兩個與色情內容有關。<br />\n<br />\n報告指出，這些帳戶很容易，也很便宜可以從經銷商處購買，通常只需幾美元。報告的共同作者托馬斯（Elise Thomas）分析，買這些帳號的人可能希望藉助大量粉絲人數，讓來自這些帳號的內容看起來更合理。<br />\n<br />\n她說，「當你滾動瀏覽推特、點擊進去看，如果看到它是上週創立的，就會看起來可疑，但如果帳號已經有五年，擁有三千或三萬個粉絲，那麼它看起來更合情合理。這就是人們購買這類帳戶的原因。」<br />\n<br />\n她警告，北京可能會繼續利用外國社交網路擴大其宣傳活動，以解決除香港以外的其它問題。"},{"pid":"b719379bc541b6557d7a7a4f4a5ced6699b0e90e","tid":1542714,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:44:41.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5EAUpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5EAUpQ.jpg&h=30bf1600&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUE1PYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUE1PYa.jpg&h=d8331036&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1sNZBDb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1sNZBDb.jpg&h=ace5c24e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8KM7Lwx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8KM7Lwx.jpg&h=5719ebc4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SoyFk4T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSoyFk4T.jpg&h=2bffae59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SsV05wz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSsV05wz.jpg&h=d54e941c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EUH604U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEUH604U.jpg&h=74590733&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d7dbea05953b3cd7298df159a5ccf816930e7dbe","tid":1542714,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:45:19.000Z","msg":"網絡戰爭<br />\n我地成班資深鍵盤戰士唔係會打輸呀？"},{"pid":"9d376ff0a468aed03c2aaad68f86e28acde8df58","tid":1542714,"uid":195169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:45:28.000Z","msg":"有冇英文版本?"},{"pid":"de549865e6d39cffa15695a137b5f102e5ede647","tid":1542714,"uid":50414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:45:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"27d35afab15af67d031e5b1c4c2e611845d74c2c","tid":1542714,"uid":277540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T02:46:47.000Z","msg":"借位用<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/562228896/posts/10156808238733897?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww